# Deployment Policy

**Never** run `vercel`, `vercel deploy`, `git push`, or any deployment command unless the user explicitly says to deploy or push.

- Make code changes locally only
- Do NOT commit or push to git after edits unless the user asks
- Do NOT trigger a Vercel deployment unless the user says something like "deploy", "push to Vercel", or "ship this"

Wait for an explicit instruction before any action that results in a deployment.
